<html lang='fr'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Stock Initialisé - {{appName}}</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f5f7fa; padding: 20px; }
      .email-container { max-width: 650px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); }
      .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b6cb0 0%, #4299e1 100%); padding: 45px 40px; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { color: #ffffff; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
      .header p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 400; }
      .content { padding: 40px; }
      .greeting { font-size: 17px; color: #1a202c; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.6; font-weight: 500; }
      .intro-text { font-size: 15px; color: #404854; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px; }
      .section-title { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; color: #2b6cb0; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-top: 28px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
      .transaction-details { background-color: #fafbfc; border: 1px solid #e8ecf1; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 6px; }
      .detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 12px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #404854; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8ecf1; }
      .detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
      .detail-label { font-weight: 600; color: #2d3748; }
      .detail-value { color: #2b6cb0; font-weight: 500; text-align: right; }
      .info-box { background-color: #ebf8ff; border-left: 4px solid #3182ce; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; color: #2a4365; line-height: 1.6; }
      .button-container { text-align: center; margin: 36px 0; }
      .button { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2b6cb0 0%, #4299e1 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 14px 45px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; transition: all 0.3s ease; border: none; cursor: pointer; }
      .footer { border-top: 1px solid #e8ecf1; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center; line-height: 1.8; }
      .footer-link { color: #2b6cb0; text-decoration: none; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='email-container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>Stock Initialisé avec Succès</h1>
        <p>Transaction #{{transactionNumber}}</p>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <div class='greeting'>Bonjour {{recipientName}},</div>
        <div class='intro-text'>
          Nous vous informons que vous avez réinitialisé le stock pour le produit <strong>{{productName}}</strong> sur le site <strong>{{siteName}}</strong>.
          Cette transaction a été automatiquement approuvée et votre stock a été mis à jour.
        </div>
        <div class='section-title'>📋 Détails de l'Initialisation</div>
        <div class='transaction-details'>
          <div class='detail-row'>
            <span class='detail-label'>Produit :&nbsp;</span>
            <span class='detail-value'>{{productName}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class='detail-row'>
            <span class='detail-label'>Quantité Ajoutée :&nbsp;</span>
            <span class='detail-value'>{{quantity}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class='detail-row'>
            <span class='detail-label'>Site :&nbsp;</span>
            <span class='detail-value'>{{siteName}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class='detail-row'>
            <span class='detail-label'>Date :&nbsp;</span>
            <span class='detail-value'>{{currentDate}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='info-box'>
          <strong>&nbsp;✅ Action terminée:</strong> Le stock est désormais disponible et prêt à être utilisé pour vos prochaines transactions.
        </div>
        <div class='button-container'>
          <a href='{{dashboardLink}}' class='button'>Voir mon Stock</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>© 2026 {{appName}}. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        <p><a href='{{dashboardLink}}' class='footer-link'>Tableau de Bord</a> | <a href='{{supportLink}}' class='footer-link'>Assistance</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
